name: MAKE NOISE REDUX
description: The celebration of the half-year mark since hic et nunc's birth (#HENOSY) prompted a revisit of my 'henesis' piece "MAKE NOISE" (OBJKT#41352) and a reflection on the growth of the platform, its community, as well as myself as an artist. This piece is a recreation of the same composition but employing a more technical aesthetic and algorithm in its execution. | Output: 1140×1140 GIF 25fps | Made in p5js | Created: 4 Sept 21 | Artist: @Yazid
